name: DJ FIXHICPLS - HEN STATE OF MIND
description:
What is up everyone? Here is a brand new trippy Vinyl with a extra chill track from "DJ FIXHICPLS"! This track is a dedicatory to all the avid hic et nunc users and their constant struggle with the platforms crashes (which happens constantly).
Is HEN crashing again? lagging or full of bugs? Just lean back, take a deep breath and relax to this electronic lo-fi'ish track!
